In contrast with the multicycle counterpart we were not able to implement the design using a single data/instruction memory, reason being during some instruction(load) when we need 
to perform memory read it sets off new decoding of data present at that location which isnot intended, further while performing memory read we need to store the Pc content while 
memory read is getting performed.

